{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01VkwmCCKk4hmLMjm5wFLNPB","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_01FDaXb6scdbFsgeiCLZFmnK","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/Users/ivintik/dev/personal/codeharness/_bmad-output/implementation-artifacts/.session-issues.md","old_string":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-20 (Session 4)","new_string":"# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-20 (Session 5)\n\n### 2-3-standalone-runtime-check-audit-mode — verify (2026-03-20T06:55Z)\n\n- **BUG FOUND: Invalid LogsQL query syntax** — `queryTelemetryEvents` used `_stream_id:*` which is not valid VictoriaLogs LogsQL. Returns HTTP 400. Fixed by changing to `*` (wildcard matching all entries).\n- **All 3 ACs PASS after fix** — validateRuntime queries backend successfully, mapEventsToModules computes 62.5% correctly, graceful skip on unreachable backend works.\n- **Stale Docker container from prior session** — had to `docker rm -f` before starting. verify-env cleanup ran between sessions but container persisted.\n- **Observability gap** — `echo ok` test command doesn't emit OTLP telemetry, so VictoriaLogs shows zero events. Expected for synthetic test commands.\n\n---\n\n# Session Issues Log — 2026-03-20 (Session 4)"},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":252,"cache_read_input_tokens":73930,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":252},"output_tokens":25,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"ea9dcd26-048d-426f-9aa1-49ae9968ed9a","uuid":"14b494e4-5515-4ed0-9b0c-2609a90f0628"}
